":2077574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425bce5013b3e4952fef4093e20221a065eb224f","tid":2077574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:09:11.000Z","msg":"證供影片不符　警：解釋唔到<br />\n<br />\n警員陳國強供稱，當晚有黑衣人堵路，惟辯方指現場影片不見有雜物，陳看片後同意，並稱「我解釋唔到」。辯方又指出，被告曾在警誡下表明沒有襲警，涉案鐵鎚亦非屬於他，陳卻稱「唔好講咁多」，而且沒記錄說話；當被告母親表明不相信其子襲警時，陳稱「警察話有就有」，並威嚇男生錄口供時「唔好講咁多嘢」。陳全部否認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200630&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20946798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200630%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20946798&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3ef85509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200630%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20946798&h=5d170e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200630&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20946798</a>"},{"pid":"58da5f7e562ed6ea2a902f98a13f6c1e1077f001","tid":2077574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"又多單<br />\n<br />\n男生否認以雨傘襲休班警 官指休班警並非誠實可靠證人，罪名不成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090219</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9918eabd4f7317a6c415ff2cc71469661d75b90a","tid":2077574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"黑警供詞與現場片段很大出入 <br />\n法官：警方要考慮告唔告作供警俾假口供<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090808</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d05805a975ef5613fcf806e771c6b8071647830","tid":20